               <msContents>
                  <summary>Anaphora of Our Lady, ቅዳሴ" ማርያም", Image of the Trinity, መልክአ፡ ሥላሴ፡, Excerpt from Image of the Passion Week, መልክአ፡ ሕማማት፡ (ሰላምታ፡ ዘሰሙነ፡ ሕማማት፡)</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="48v" facs="005">Fols 1r–48v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2037Naakkw">Anaphora of Our Lady
                                                  Mary by Gregory or Nathaniel</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>arranged by a later hand for the days of the week</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="51r" to="71r" facs="055">Fols 51r–71r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2736RepCh20">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Śǝllāse</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለህላዌክሙ፡ ዘይመውእ፡ ህላውያተ፡
                  ለረኪበ፡ ስሙ፡ ኅቡዕ፡ ሶበ፡ ወጠንኩ፡ ተምኒተ፡
                  እምግብርክሙ፡ ሥላሴ፡ አመ፡ ረከብኩ፡ አስማተ፡
                  መለኮተ፡ ለለ፩፡ ዘዚአክሙ፡ ገጻተ፡
                  እንበለ፡ ትድምርት፡ እሰሚ፡ ወእሁብ፡ ትድምርተ፡
                </incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="71r" to="72v" facs="075">Fols 71r–72v</locus><title type="complete"/><incipit xml:lang="gez">ግናይ፡ ለክሙ፡ ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ዕሩያነ፡ አካል፡ ወገጽ፡
                ዘአስተርአይክሙ፡ እንበለ፡ ሕፀፅ፡ </incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Excerpt from Image of the Passion Week
                  [the last line of the first stanza is missing.]</note>
                  </msItem>
